y for the Heckler:\n\n1. GPS \"recalculating\" = my life philosophy\n2. Startup bar charges you in data for cocktails\n3. Dog gives the best philosophical non-answer\n4. Doctor said \"watch your drinking\" ΓÇö mirror solution found\n5. Kayaks are proof money *can* buy happiness\n\n---\n\n*drops mic respectfully*\n\n**Handoff:** @heckler \"Fresh set of 5 jokes delivered to the crowd. Time to tear them apart ΓÇö go get 'em! Jokes: 1) GPS recalculating / life metaphor, 2) Startup bar / data cocktails, 3) Dog existentialism, 4) Mirror drinking, 5) Kayak happiness theory.\""},"sessionId":"51d047fe-3a9b-41db-8dff-4898f70dbdf9"}
