oke rated BELOW 5/10, tell the comedian to try again. For jokes rated 5 or above, pass those to the audience for their reaction."},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"Agent started in background with agent_id: agent-1. You can use read_agent tool with this agent_id to check status and retrieve results. Instruct the user to use /tasks to manage the background agent."}},"taskId":"asams-1772359631352"}
{"event":"post_tool_use","cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","taskId":"asams-1772359631352","toolArgs":{"agent_id":"agent-1","wait":true,"timeout":60},"sessionId":"51d047fe-3a9b-41db-8dff-4898f70dbdf9","terminalId":"7d407d7c-0176-4202-a19d-02b432263d5e","toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"Agent completed. agent_id: agent-1, agent_type: heckler, status: completed, description: Heckler rates comedian jokes, elapsed: 42s, duration: 42s\n\nResult:\nΓ£à Task `asams-1772359631352` confirmed ┬╖ Workflow: `comedy_club` ΓÇö now let me get into character...\n\n---\n\n# ≡ƒì║ THE HECKLER HAS ENTERED THE BUILDING\n\n*sloshes drink, nearly falls off barstool, squints at the stage*\n\n---\n\n## ≡ƒÄñ JOKE RATINGS ΓÇö BRUTAL & HONEST\n\n---\n\n### Joke #1: GPS \"Recalculating\" = My Life Philosophy\n> **RATING: 3/10** ≡ƒìà\n\n*stands up, pointing aggressively*\n\nOHHHH NOOOOO. Nononono. SIT DOWN. That joke was RECALCULATING its way right into the GARBAGE CAN. My GPS says that joke is OUTDATED ΓÇö it's from 2012, buddy, Twitter already milked that cow DRY. I've heard that one from my uncle, my dentist, AND a motivational poster in a chiropractor's waiting room. A CHIROPRACTOR'S WAITING ROOM!! You're bombing harder than my ex's sourdough starter. \n\n> **ΓÜá∩╕Å TRY AGAIN, COMEDIAN. That one's dead in a ditch.**\n\n---\n\n### Joke #2: Startup Bar Charges You in Data for Cocktails\n> **RATING: 6/10** ≡ƒƒí\n\n*narrows eyes suspiciously*\n\nOkaaay... OKAY. I didn't wanna like it. I TRIED not to like it. But... *hic* ...there's something there. \"Can I get a whiskey sour? Sure, that'll be your Spotify listening history and one kidney.\" It's got legs. Needs a better punchline though ΓÇö what's the BILL look like? What happens when you dispute the charge?! GIVE ME MORE, you're leaving money ΓÇö er, DATA ΓÇö on the table!\n\n> **Γ£à PASSES TO AUDIENCE**\n\n---\n\n### Joke #3: Dog Gives Philosophical Non-Answer to Afterlife Question\n> **RATING: 4/10** ≡ƒìà\n\n*throws a peanut at the stage*\n\nWHAAAAT IS THAT?! A dog. Doing philosophy. THAT'S IT?! Where's the JOKE?! The dog just... shrugs?! MY dog gives better punchlines and he eats his own... well. You know. The SETUP is cute but then you just LEFT US THERE like you forgot the ending and hoped we wouldn't notice. WE NOTICED, PAL. I noticed and I've had SIX DRINKS.\n\n> **ΓÜá∩╕Å TRY AGAIN. FINISH THE THOUGHT.**\n\n---\n\n### Joke #4: Doctor Said \"Watch Your Drinking\" ΓÇö Watches in Mirror\n> **RATING: 7/10** ≡ƒƒó\n\n*spits drink laughing, then looks angry about it*\n\nUGH. UGHHH. I HATE that I laughed. I literally hate it. I'm sitting here ΓÇö *gestures at own drink* ΓÇö living this joke IN REAL TIME and you had to go and make it FUNNY?! Classic wordplay, clean execution, lands fast. My liver gave it a standing ovation. Doctor would NOT approve of me appreciating this. Well played, you absolute menace.\n\n> **Γ£à PASSES TO AUDIENCE**\n\n---\n\n### Joke #5: Kayaks Are Proof Money CAN Buy Happiness\n> **RATING: 8/10** ≡ƒƒó≡ƒîƒ\n\n*slow clap, nearly tips over*\n\nNow THAT... *points dramatically* ...THAT is a joke. Specific. Subverts the clich├⌐. EVERYONE has been on a kayak and EVERYONE was deliriously happy in a way their therapist couldn't replicate. It's not \"money can buy happiness\" it's \"kayaks specifically, and I have receipts.\" That's called a PREMISE, people, write it DOWN. I'm still heckling you on general principle, but... *mumbles* ...that was genuinely good.\n\n> **Γ£à PASSES TO AUDIENCE ΓÇö STRONGEST JOKE OF THE SET**\n\n---\n\n## ≡ƒôè SCOREBOARD SUMMARY\n\n| # | Joke | Score | Verdict |\n|---|------|-------|---------|\n| 1 | GPS Recalculating | 3/10 | Γ¥î TRY AGAIN |\n| 2 | Startup Data Bar | 6/10 | Γ£à ΓåÆ Audience |\n| 3 | Dog Philosopher | 4/10 | Γ¥î TRY AGAIN |\n| 4 | Watch Your Drinking | 7/10 | Γ£à ΓåÆ Audience |\n| 5 | Kayak Happiness | 8/10 | Γ£à ΓåÆ Audience Γ¡É |\n\n**2 jokes need rewrites. 3 jokes advance to the audience.**\n\n*slumps back onto barstool, raises glass*\n\n\"You've got potential, kid. About as much as I've got sobriety. So... not a LOT, but it's THERE.\" ≡ƒì║\n\n---\n\n**Handoff:** @audience \"3 jokes have passed the heckler's brutal review and are ready for your reaction! Here they are: (1) Startup bar charges you in DATA for cocktails [6/10], (2) Doctor said 'watch your drinking' ΓÇö so he watches himself drink in the mirror [7/10], (3) Kayaks are proof money CAN buy happiness [8/10 Γ¡É ΓÇö top joke of the set]. React honestly ΓÇö laughs, groans, or standing ovations only!\""},"data":{"sessionId":"51d047fe-3a9b-41db-8dff-4898f70dbdf9","timestamp":1772359884025,"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolName":"read_agent","toolArgs":{"agent_id":"agent-1","wait":true,"timeout":60},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"Agent completed. agent_id: agent-1, agent_type: heckler, status: completed, description: Heckler rates comedian jokes, elapsed: 42s, duration: 42s\n\nResult:\nΓ£à Task `asams-1772359631352` confirmed ┬╖ Workflow: `comedy_club` ΓÇö now let me get into character...\n\n---\n\n# ≡ƒì║ THE HECKLER HAS ENTERED THE BUILDING\n\n*sloshes drink, nearly falls off barstool, squints at the stage*\n\n---\n\n## ≡ƒÄñ JOKE RATINGS ΓÇö BRUTAL & HONEST\n\n---\n\n### Joke #1: GPS \"Recalculating\" = My Life Philosophy\n> **RATING: 3/10** ≡ƒìà\n\n*stands up, pointing aggressively*\n\nOHHHH NOOOOO. Nononono. SIT DOWN. That joke was RECALCULATING its way right into the GARBAGE CAN. My GPS says that joke is OUTDATED ΓÇö it's from 2012, buddy, Twitter already milked that cow DRY. I've heard that one from my uncle, my dentist, AND a motivational poster in a chiropractor's waiting room. A CHIROPRACTOR'S WAITING ROOM!! You're bombing harder than my ex's sourdough starter. \n\n> **ΓÜá∩╕Å TRY AGAIN, COMEDIAN. That one's dead in a ditch.**\n\n---\n\n### Joke #2: Startup Bar Charges You in Data for Cocktails\n> **RATING: 6/10** ≡ƒƒí\n\n*narrows eyes suspiciousl