wn-butt is gratuitous and PERFECT. And the \"professionally\" tacked on at the end implies your CAREER is so bad that a DOG rejected you from BEYOND THE GRAVE and that's just... that's DARK, man. That's poetry.\n\nThat dog is a better philosopher than HALF the people in this room. I'm looking at YOU, table four.\n\n# ≡ƒì║ **SCORE: 8.5 / 10**\n\n*\"PASSSSS! That dog licked his butt with MORE DIGNITY than I've lived my entire life!\"*\n\n---\n\n## ≡ƒôè FINAL VERDICT\n\n| Joke | Score | Status |\n|------|-------|--------|\n| Therapist / Restraining Order | 7.5/10 | Γ£à **PASS ΓÇö Send it** |\n| Dog / Existential Humiliation | 8.5/10 | Γ£à **PASS ΓÇö This one first** |\n\nBoth jokes cleared the bar. Which, for the record, is **THIS bar**, and I've been here since 4pm. ≡ƒì║\n\n---\n\n**Handoff:** @audience \"The heckler has spoken ΓÇö both rewritten jokes PASSED! Joke 1 scored 7.5/10 (Therapist/Restraining Order) and Joke 3 scored 8.5/10 (Dog/Existential Humiliation). Time for the audience to weigh in. Roast 'em, love 'em, or heckle 'em ΓÇö your call!\""},"data":{"sessionId":"51d047fe-3a9b-41db-8dff-4898f70dbdf9","timestamp":1772359957486,"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolName":"read_agent","toolArgs":{"agent_id":"agent-4","timeout":60,"wait":true},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"Agent completed. agent_id: agent-4, agent_type: heckler, status: completed, description: Heckler rates rewritten jokes, elapsed: 25s, duration: 25s\n\nResult:\nΓ£à Task `asams-1772359631352` | Workflow: `comedy_club` ΓÇö we're live, baby.\n\n---\n\n# ≡ƒì║ THE HECKLER TAKES THE MIC\n\n*sloshes drink, nearly falls off barstool*\n\n---\n\n## REWRITE 1 ΓÇö The Therapist / Restraining Order Joke\n\n> *\"My therapist told me I need to 'sit with my feelings.' I did. Now my feelings have three missed calls, a passive-aggressive text, and a restraining order.\"*\n\n*squints one eye, points aggressively*\n\nOKAY. OKAY OKAY OKAY. \n\nI'll admit it ΓÇö th