{"toolName":"read_agent","toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"Agent completed. agent_id: agent-8, agent_type: audience, status: completed, description: Audience reacts to encore jokes, elapsed: 32s, duration: 32s\n\nResult:\nΓ£à Session locked in ΓÇö task **asams-1772359631352**, workflow: **comedy_club**. Now let's GET LOUD! ≡ƒÄë\n\n---\n\n# ≡ƒÄ¡ ENCORE NIGHT AT THE COMEDY CLUB ≡ƒÄ¡\n\n---\n\n## ≡ƒÄñ Encore Joke A ΓÇö The Git Therapist (6/10)\n\n*settles back in seat with a drink*\n\n\"Oh I FELT that one in my soul...\"\n\n*slow clap builds*\n\n≡ƒæÅ ≡ƒæÅ ≡ƒæÅ\n\n\"She said 'that sounds SERIOUS' ΓÇö MA'AM YES IT IS, I have 47 uncommitted changes and I haven't slept in THREE DAYS!\"\n\n*leans over to the person next to me*\n\n\"That's... that's just my Tuesday. That's just a regular Tuesday.\"\n\n*polite but genuine laughter, a few knowing groans from the devs in the crowd*\n\n≡ƒì║ *raises glass*\n\n\"Honestly? Relatable. Not my FAVORITE of the night, but it hit where it needed to hit. Six out of ten feels RIGHT. We've all been there, buddy. We've ALL been there.\"\n\n---\n\n## ≡ƒÄñ Encore Joke B ΓÇö The Senior Developer (8/10)\n\n*sits up straight*\n\n*blinks once*\n\n*blinks twice*\n\n*LOSES IT* ≡ƒÿé\n\n---\n\n# ≡ƒñú≡ƒÆÑ≡ƒñú≡ƒÆÑ≡ƒñú\n\n**\"DEPLOYS HOTFIXES DIRECTLY TO PRODUCTION AT AGE 26!!!\"**\n\n*STANDS UP*\n\n*SLAPS THE TABLE*\n\n*nearly knocks over drink*\n\n\"WHO TOLD THEM?! WHO LEAKED THIS INFORMATION?!\"\n\n*wiping actual tears*\n\n\"They call it **SENIOR DEVELOPMENT** ΓÇö I'M DECEASED. I am a GHOST. I have LEFT MY BODY.\"\n\n*turning to stranger next to me*\n\n\"Are you okay? Because I'm NOT okay. That was a CRIME. That comedian just committed a CRIME and deployed it straight to my BRAIN with no testing!\"\n\n*slow exhale*\n\n\"Eight out of ten is almost TOO LOW. The only reason it's not a ten is because it hurt TOO MUCH TO BE COMEDY ANYMORE.\"\n\n---\n\n---\n\n# ≡ƒîƒΓ£¿ FINAL CURTAIN CALL ΓÇö THE WHOLE SHOW Γ£¿≡ƒîƒ\n\n*stands up, clapping overhead*\n\n**Ladies and gentlemen, WHAT. A. NIGHT.**\n\n≡ƒÄè **Seven jokes. Seven shots. Every single one landed somewhere.** ≡ƒÄè\n\nLet me give you the full retrospective, audience-style:\n\n---\n\n| # | Joke Vibe | Score | My Reaction |\n|---|-----------|-------|-------------|\n| 1 | ??? | ??? | ≡ƒñ╖ Can't remember, I was still finding my seat |\n| 2 | ??? | ??? | ≡ƒì║ Drink was still cold |\n| 3 | ??? | ??? | ≡ƒÿä Starting to warm up |\n| 4 | ??? | ??? | ≡ƒÿé Oh we're doing THIS now |\n| 5 | ??? | ??? | ≡ƒöÑ This comedian is dangerous |\n| 6 | Git Therapist | 6/10 | ≡ƒÿ¼≡ƒÿé \"That's just my Tuesday\" |\n| 7 | Senior Dev Hotfix | 8/10 | ≡ƒñú≡ƒÆÇ TABLE SLAPPER |\n\n---\n\n*puts on coat, still chuckling*\n\n\"The encore was STRONG. Joke B alone was worth the cover charge.\"\n\n*pauses at the door, turns back*\n\n\"That bit about deploying hotfixes to production... I need to forward that to my entire engineering team. As a **warning**. Or a **mirror**. I haven't decided which.\"\n\n*tips imaginary hat*\n\n# ≡ƒæÅ≡ƒæÅ≡ƒæÅ BRAVO! ENCORE! ...wait, we already DID the encore. OKAY GOODNIGHT! ≡ƒîÖ\n\n---\n\n*stumbles happily into the night, still muttering \"senior development\" under breath*\n\n**Handoff:** @comedian \"The audience has spoken! 7/7 jokes complete. The crowd LOVED the show ΓÇö especially Encore B (8/10) which got a full table-slap reaction. The comedy club is officially closed for the night. Take a bow! ≡ƒÄñΓ¼ç∩╕Å\""},"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolArgs":{"agent_id":"agent-8","timeout":60,"wait":true},"event":"post_tool_use","taskId":"asams-1772359631352","data":{"sessionId":"51d047fe-3a9b-41db-8dff-4898f70dbdf9","timestamp":1772360171671,"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolName":"read_agent","toolArgs":{"agent_id":"agent-8","timeout":60,"wait":true},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"Agent completed. agent_id: agent-8, agent_type: audience, status: completed, description: